她以 1997 年的热门歌曲“That Don&#39;t Impress Me Much”拉开了序幕。 </p><figure id="attachment_3770640" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3770640" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3770640" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/shania-twain-glastonbury@2000x1270.jpg" alt="仙妮亚·唐恩 (Shania Twain) 于 2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节第五天在金字塔舞台上表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/shania-twain-glastonbury@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/shania-twain-glastonbury@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/shania-twain-glastonbury@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/shania-twain-glastonbury@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/shania-twain-glastonbury@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/shania-twain-glastonbury@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3770640" class="wp-caption-text">仙妮亚·唐恩 (Shania Twain) 在 2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节上表演。图片来源：Joe Maher/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>然而， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/social-media-reacts-to-shania-twain-set-at-glastonbury-2024-3770637">国内观众批评了该剧的声音问题</a>。<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/shania-twain-glastonbury-2024-setlist-photos-3770685">阅读<em>NME 对</em>吐温在 2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节上的“高调音乐富矿”的三星级评论</a>。</p><h2> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-heres-what-sza-played-to-close-out-the-show-3770815">尽管技术困难，SZA 在周末最后一场金字塔头条比赛中表现出色</a></h2><p>SZA 为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/szas-headlining-glastonbury-set-plagued-by-technical-difficulties-social-media-reacts-3770821">Glastonbury 2024 带来了一场极具魅力的决赛头条表演</a>，充满了时代和美学的视觉跳跃——但<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/szas-headlining-glastonbury-set-plagued-by-technical-difficulties-social-media-reacts-3770821">不幸的是，她的布景也因麦克风和浑浊的声音而受到技术困难的困扰</a>。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/sza-live-at-glastonbury-2024-setlist-review-photos-3770784">阅读<em>NME 对</em>SZA 在 2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节上的头条新闻的四星评论</a>。</p><h2>伦敦文法学校将乔治·菲茨杰拉德带入公园舞台决赛</h2><p>距上次在格拉斯顿伯里亮相十年后，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/london-grammar">伦敦文法学校</a>重返沃西农场。这支电子流行乐队以<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/george-fitzgerald">乔治·菲茨杰拉德（George Fitzgerald</a> ）的《宝贝就是你》（Baby It&#39;s You）结束了公园舞台，汉娜·里德（Hannah Reid）宣称他们的嘉宾不仅是“音乐界最友善的人，而且是最有才华的人”。</p><h2> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-the-national-perform-mesmerising-set-with-kate-stables-as-a-special-guest-3770858">The National 在 Other Stage 的闭场演出中推出了 This Is The Kit 的 Kate Stables</a></h2><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-national">国家乐队</a>在 Other Stage 的闭幕演出中为《Rylan》带来了 Kate Stables（又名<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/this-is-the-kit">This Is The Kit）</a> 。 </p><figure id="attachment_3770897" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3770897" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3770897" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/NME_Glasto24_TheNational_Other_AFord-62423.jpg" alt="2024 年格拉斯顿伯里国家音乐节现场演出。图片来源：NME 的 Andy Ford" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/NME_Glasto24_TheNational_Other_AFord-62423.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/NME_Glasto24_TheNational_Other_AFord-62423-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/NME_Glasto24_TheNational_Other_AFord-62423-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/NME_Glasto24_TheNational_Other_AFord-62423-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/NME_Glasto24_TheNational_Other_AFord-62423-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/NME_Glasto24_TheNational_Other_AFord-62423-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 200