wp-content/uploads/2024/06/NMEGlasto24_Coldplay_Pyramid_AFord-60152-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/NMEGlasto24_Coldplay_Pyramid_AFord-60152-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/NMEGlasto24_Coldplay_Pyramid_AFord-60152-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3770520" class="wp-caption-text">酷玩乐队 (Coldplay) 在 2024 年格拉斯顿伯里 (Glastonbury) 现场演出。图片来源：NME 的 Andy Ford</figcaption></figure><p> “休耕年之前的节日总是一个有趣的计划，因为你几乎必须将两年融入其中，”伊维斯谈到明年的节日时说道。</p><p>伊维斯在回顾今年沃西农场的狂欢时说：“这一定是迄今为止最好的一次。我们庞大而令人难以置信的工作人员中的每一位对于使这项活动顺利进行都至关重要。当然，如果没有善良、才华横溢、受人尊敬的节日观众的参与，它根本就不会存在。</p><p> 2024 年的格拉斯顿伯里音乐节现已落下帷幕， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/szas-headlining-glastonbury-set-plagued-by-technical-difficulties-social-media-reacts-3770821">尽管存在技术问题</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/sza-live-at-glastonbury-2024-setlist-review-photos-3770784">SZA 在金字塔舞台上奉献了四星级的头条表演</a>，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/the-national-live-glastonbury-2024-review-setlist-photos-3770895">国民乐队则在其他舞台上奉献了五星级的闭幕表演</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3770303" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3770303" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3770303" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/NMEGlasto24_Kasabian_Woodsies_AFord-620403.jpg" alt="Kasabian 在 Glastonbury 2024 现场演出。图片来源：NME 的 Andy Ford" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/NMEGlasto24_Kasabian_Woodsies_AFord-620403.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/NMEGlasto24_Kasabian_Woodsies_AFord-620403-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/NMEGlasto24_Kasabian_Woodsies_AFord-620403-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/NMEGlasto24_Kasabian_Woodsies_AFord-620403-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/NMEGlas